705831f-a.title: Brooklyn: Navy Street - Park Avenue
705831f-a.text:
Navy Street, west side, between Park Ave., and Tillary Street.
October 31, 1927.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.

705832f-a.title: Brooklyn: Navy Street - Tillary Street
705832f-a.text:
Navy Street, north from Tillary Street, toward the Brooklyn
Navy Yark. Views 2,3 are at Johnson Street and show demoliton
for the erection of Fort Greene Houses.
P. L. Sperr  View 1: August 23, 1939
NO REPRIDUCTIONS  View 2,3: April 22, 1941
